<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">When to Exchange Tiles</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-green-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">🎯 Exchange Decision Rule</p>
  <p class="text-base text-gray-200">Exchange when your EV Score is <span class="text-white font-medium">below 30</span> AND you cannot score 20+ points on this turn. Exchanging costs one turn but typically raises your next rack's EV by 30-50 points — a massive improvement in scoring potential over the following 2-3 turns.</p>
</div>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/10">
